dataset_id: Aquarius L3 Weekly Polar-Gridded Sea Surface Salinity V005
title: Aquarius L3 Weekly Polar-Gridded Sea Surface Salinity V005
summary: This data set consists of weekly gridded Level-3 products of Aquarius L-band radiometer Sea Surface Salinity (SSS) retrievals from the Aquarius/Satélite de Aplicaciones Científicas (SAC-D) mission, developed collaboratively between the U.S. National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) and Argentina's space agency, Comisión Nacional de Actividades Espaciales (CONAE).
